    AbstractBatchBugTrackerPlugin
    This is the abstract class from which all plugins implementing BatchBugTrackerPlugin would extend.
    AbstractBugTrackerAndChangesetDiscoveryPlugin Deprecated.
    Instead of implementing this interface, plugin can calculate candidate changesets before filing the bug using fields in BugSubmission.getIssueDetail(), namely getLastBuildWithoutIssue(), getFileName() and getDetectedInBuild()

    This is the abstract class from which all plugins implementing BugTrackerPlugin would extend.
